  Sin3-kiat siuN7-tioh8 ti7 soaN-teng2 bo5 chhiu7-a2 e5 soaN, lai5 cheng3 ou5-tho5 thang pang-chan7 song3-hiong e5 lang5, na7 khah hng7 chiah eng7 ‘sian5 e5 sit8-a2’. Sin3-kiat chiu7 ti7 am3-mi5, ti7 seh e5 tiong-kan, ti7 thih-lou7 piN tit8-tit8 cheng3, chiaN5-cho3 chhiu7-na5. Keh chit8-mi5, thau3-cha2 khi2-lai5, ou5-tho5-a2 lak-loh8 tioh8 chhu3-teng2, chhin-chhiuN7 teh tim3 chioh8-thau5. Pa-pa tioh8 chit8-kiaN chhut-khi3 khoaN3-mai7, koh khah tioh8-kiaN, chit8 mi5 e5 tiong-kan chhu3-piN long2 piN3-cho3 ou5-tho5 e5 chhiu7-na5, chiu7 chau2 jip8 chhu3-lai7 kong2, “Sin3-kiat, Sin3-kiat chin ki5-koai3 ah, cha-mi5 chit8-mi5 e5 tiong-kan lan2 chia chiu7 piN3 ou5-tho5 e5 chhiu7-na5 lah. Hou3! Goa2 taN na7 khioh chiah-e5 ou5-tho5, chiu7 pi2 nia2 geh8-kip khah ho2.” 
