  Seh iuN5 lah, seh e5 chui2 chiu7 chiaN5-choe3 toa7 chui2, pa-pa tak8-jit8 ui7-tioh8 hiah-e5 siu7 chui2-chai e5 cho3-sit-lang5 khoa3-lu7. Sin3-kiat chiah siuN7-tioh8 “sian5 e5 sit8-a2” tioh8 ti7 chit-e5 si5-chun7 lai5 eng7, chiu7 tui3 pa-pa kong2 beh chhut-khi3 chit8-e7, tui3 au7-bin7 chhut-khi3 sui5-si5 koa3 “sian5 e5 sit8-a2”. 
  Ki5-biau7 ah, Sin3-kiat chhin-chhiuN7 hui-ki chiu7 poe-khi3, koh chhin-chhiuN7 se3-chiah chiau2-a2 kap sian5 e7-thang theng5 ti7 kek8 se3-ki e5 chhiu7-boe2. Chong2-si7 Sin3-kiat siuN7-tioh8 i m7-thang cho3 ka-ki7 e5 lou7-eng7, chiu7 tak8 sou2-chai7 poe beh chiong ou5-tho5-a2 pun hou7 hiah-e5 bo5 mih8 thang chiah8 e5 lang5. Ti7 e7-bin7 chin che7 thih-lou7 e5 kang-lang5 teh siu-li2 thih-lou7, chong2-si7 ia7 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 Sin3-kiat, in-ui7 Sin3-kiat e5 seng-khu piN3 chhin-chhiuN7 sian5 hiah-nih8 se3. 
  Sin3-kiat chiu7 poe-kau3 hiah-e5 in-ui7 toa7-chui2 bo5 mih8 thang chiah8 e5 lang5 e5 chhu3-teng2, tui3 lai7-bin7 hoah kong2 “Oeh, oeh! Lin2 u7 khiam3-eng7 chiah8-mih8 bo5?” Tui3 lai7-bin7 in3 kong2, “Ouh, sim2-mih8 lang5 ah, u7 khiam3-kheh ouh, bo5 chui2 thang lim, ia7 bo5 chiah8-mih8.” Sin3-kiat chiu7 sui5-si5 tui3 te7-a2 lai7 theh8-chhut i e5 “ou5-tho5-a2” chhut-lai5 ki5-to2, ti7 lang5 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 chhu3-teng2 haiN3 chhut ou5-tho5-a2 chha-put-to chit8 tau2. Chiong hiah-e5 theh8 jip8-khi3 hou7 in kong2, chhiaN2 lin2 chiah8 che. “Chui2 na7 the3, lin2 chiong chi2 cheng3 ti7 chhan5-hng5 chiu7 e7 pang-chan7 lin2 e5 seng-oah8”. Sin3-kiat chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni seh8 chha-put-to 100 keng e5 chhu3, keh-jit8 Sin3-kiat tui3 hak8-hau7 tng2-lai5, ka7 pa-pa kong2 beh chhut-khi3 thit-tho5, chiu7 koh khi3 tham3 hiah-e5 siu7 chai-hai7 e5 cho3-sit-lang5, chiong chiah8-mih8 pun hou7 in. Chit-e5 tai7-chi3 chiaN5-cho3 toa7 hong-siaN: “He si7 thiN-sai3 lah, hit-e5 gin2-na2 u7 hoat-sit8 neh!” 
  Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 be7-thang ti7 jit8-si5 poe ti7 khong-tiong khi3 tham3 hiah-e5 cho3-sit-lang5, jit8 loh8-soaN i2-au7 am3-chiN7 khi3. Chong2-si7 cho3-sit-lang5 in-ui7 kiaN bo5 lang5 kaN2 ka7 i khui mng5. Sin3-kiat chiu7 chiong chit8 tau2 ou5-tho5-a2 khng3 ti7 chhu3-teng2. Sin3-kiat pun ou5-tho5-a2 hou7 siu7 chui2-chai e5 cho3-sit-lang5 e5 te7 7 mi5, u7 cho3-sit-lang5 siuN7 beh liah8 thiN-sai3 cho3 sim-sek, chiu7 chio-chip8 chng lai7 e5 chheng-lian5 3, 4 e5 bih ti7 hia teh theng3-hau7 Sin3-kiat khi3. Sin3-kiat long2 m7 chai-iaN2, kau3-ui7 kong2, “Oeh, bo5 chiah8-mih8, ou5-tho5-a2 hou7 lin2”, beh jip8-khi3 e5 si5, in chiu7 ka7 i liah8-teh kong2, “Li2 u7 hoat-sit8, u7-iaN2 bo5?” U7-e5 mng7 kong2 “Li2 si7 lang5 a2-si7 kui2? Li2 thai2 u7 hiah che7 ou5-tho5-a2? Li2 ia7 bo5 chun5, ia7 bo5 chhia, tui3 to2-ui7 chai3 lai5?” Toa7 siaN se3 siaN teh ka7 i mng7. In chiu7 ka7 i chhia-to2, chiong saN long2 ka7 i thng3 khi2-lai5, kong2 “Li2 to bo5 hoat-sit8 ah!” “Chit-e5 ma7 bo5 siN boe2, chong2-si7 u7 ki5-koai3 e5 mih8, ou5-tho5-a2, chhau2-tek8 kap sian5 e5 sit8-a2. Ki5-koai3 e5 gin2-na2 ah, che beh cho3 sim2-mih8?” In lun5-liu5 khoaN3 hiah-e5 mih8. Ki5-tiong chit8 e5 khui2-khiat e5 chheng-lian5 kong2, “Chit liap8 tho5-a2, kiam2-chhai2 si7 teh pian3 ki5-sut8 e5, lan2 lai5 ka7 cham7 hou7 phoa3 khoaN3-mai7”. Sin3-kiat giong7 beh khau3, ka7 in kong2, “ChhiaN2 goan5-liong7 leh, he si7 goa2 e5 po2-poe3, m7-thang ka7 goa2 long3 hai7.” 
  Hit si5 e5 chheng-lian5 chiu7 ju2 ai3 beh long3 phoa3 ou5-tho5-a2, Sin3-kiat siuN7, na7 hou7 in long3 phoa3 chiu7 hai7 lah, koaN2 kin2 khioh lak ti7 thou5-kha e5 chhau2-tek8 pun5 chit8 siaN, “Pit8-pit8”. Hut-jian5-kan chin iong2 e5 chhin-chhiuN7 eng-a2, niau-thau5-chiau2......poe lai5 thong2 hiah-e5 chheng-lian5, chheng-lian5 tioh8 chit8-kiaN chiong ou5-tho5-a2 hiat tui3 chui2-te2 loh8-khi3, Sin3-kiat chiu7 koh koaN2-kin2 khioh sit8-a2 poe tui3 khong-tiong khi3, chhiaN2 chiau2-a2 ka7 i khioh ou5-tho5-a2 khi2-lai5. KhoaN3 kau3 gang7 e5 chheng-lian5 kong2, “Aih ah! Be7-thang cho3 phaiN2 tai7-chi3, Siong7-te3 teh heng5-hoat8 lan2. Chha chit8-sut-a2 goa2 e5 bak8-chiu chiu7 khi3 hou7 thong2 chhiN-mi5!” Chit-e5 siau-sit thoan5 kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7, chiu7 chin che7 lang5 beh lai5 khoaN3 chit-e5 ki5-koai3 e5 e7 poe e5 lang5. 
