  Sin3-kiat u7 chit8-e5 ng3-bang7, chiu7-si7 kap chiau2-a2 peng5-iu2 kau3 chin-hng7 khi3 thit-tho5. U7 chit8-jit8 pa-pa khi3 ke-nih8 be2 mih8 e5 si5, Sin3-kiat pun5 chhau2-tek8 chio-chip8 chiau2-a2 phoaN7 chiu7 eng7 sian5 e5 sit8-a2 khi3 soaN-lai7 thit-tho5. 
  Hit jit8 thiN-khi3 chin ho2 sit8-chai7 chin ho2 thit-tho5 e5 jit8, Sin3-kiat soah be7 ki3-tit sian5 e5 hoan-hu3, ti7 soaN-lai7 chau2-sio-jiok, ng-kok8-ke, thiau3-bu2. Kau3 tiong-tau3 e5 si5, Sin3-kiat soah phah m7-kiN3 po2-poe3 e5 ou5-tho5-a2. “Ah! Hai7 lah, po2-poe3 phah m7-kiN3 lah!” It-tit8 chhoe7, chhoe7 bo5, chiau2-a2-phoaN7 ia7 ka7 i tau3 chhoe7, in-ui7 soaN chin toa7, khah chhoe7 to chhoe7 bo5. Teh chhoe7 e5 tiong-kan chin po2-poe3 e5 “sian5 e5 sit8-a2” koh bo5--khi3, Sin3-kiat chiu7 bo5 hoat-tou7 koh poe khi3 khong-tiong, Sin3-kiat chiah siuN7-tioh8 sian5 e5 hoan-hu3. Sin3-kiat chiu7 ti7 hia kiu5 Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2. Siu7 hoan-hu3 tioh8 eng7 cho3 pang-chan7 lang5 e5, i theh8-lai5 cho3 ka-ki7 thit-tho5 e5 khi3-khu7, sit8-chai7 m7 tioh8. I siuN7 an2-ni chiu7 tng2-khi3 chhu3-nih8, pa-pa thiaN-tioh8 an2-ni, ia7 tak8 sou2-chai7 khi3 chhoe7, chong2-si7 long2 chhoe7 bo5. 
  Chong2-si7, kai-chai3, i2-keng u7 cho7 chin-che7 ou5-tho5-a2 e5 chhiu7-na5, Sin3-kiat kap pa-pa m7-bian2 hoan5-lo2 chiah8-mih8, koh e7-thang pang-chan7, khiam3-khoeh chiah8-mih8 e5 lang5, hou7 in hoaN-hi2. 
  Sin3-kiat chiam7-chiam7 toa7-han7 chiu7 ti7 Toa7-seh soaN-kha khui chit8 e5 chin khoah e5 bok8-tiuN5, chit8-si3-lang5 eng7 ‘chhau2-tek8’ kap soaN-lai7 e5 chiau2-a2 cho3 peng5-iu2. 
